channel.title: Log in Problems
channel.description: Ok so i started a 562 server. Everythings up i checked server status it says online. i even got client. So i made myself owner and edited everything i wanted and logged in (localhost). once i did all that i remembered that only i could log in b/c i was using local host. so i edited the client to put in my server ip and it says error connecting to server even though its up? i changed everything in source files and client files to my server ip. still nothing. it only lets me log in as localhost but my server is online? what did i do wrong or what did i forget to do to make it not log in?
